'''Hugh Roberts''' (born September 27, 1992) is an American [[soccer]] player who currently plays for [[Charlotte Independence]] in the [[USL Championship]].

==Club career==

===College===
Roberts played [[college soccer]] at [[George Mason University]] between 2010 and 2013.<ref name="gomason">{{cite web|url=http://www.gomason.com/ViewArticle.dbml?ATCLID=205055989&|title=Hugh Roberts Bio - GoMason.com - The Official Athletic Site Of George Mason University|publisher=gomason.com|accessdate=2014-05-02}}</ref>

While at college, Roberts played for [[USL PDL]] club [[Baltimore Bohemians]] during their 2012 and 2013 seasons.<ref name="soccerstats">{{cite web|url=http://soccerstats.us/bios/hugh-roberts/|title=Hugh Roberts &#124; SoccerStats.us|publisher=soccerstats.us|accessdate=2014-05-02}}</ref>

===Professional===
Roberts signed with [[USL Pro]] club [[Richmond Kickers]] on March 7, 2013.<ref name="richmondkickers">{{cite web|url=http://www.richmondkickers.com/home/792952.html|title=KICKERS SIGN HUGH ROBERTS - Richmond Kickers|publisher=richmondkickers.com|accessdate=2014-05-02}}</ref> After three seasons with the Kickers, Roberts became a regular starter on the backline making 79 total appearances and scoring twice. During the [[2016 Richmond Kickers season|2016 season]], Roberts was named to the USL All-League First Team.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uslsoccer.com/news_article/show/710622?referrer_id=2424360|title=2016 USL All-League Teams Unveiled|publisher=USLsoccer.com|date=2016-10-18|accessdate=2016-12-28}}</ref>

Roberts signed with [[United Soccer League|USL]] club [[Bethlehem Steel FC]] on December 22, 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bethlehemsteelfc.com/news_article/show/737097?referrer_id=2449180|title=Bethlehem Steel FC Signs Defender Hugh Roberts|publisher=Bethlehem Steel FC|date=2016-12-22|accessdate=2016-12-28}}</ref>

On January 10, 2019, Roberts joined USL Championship side [[Charlotte Independence]].<ref>https://www.charlotteindependence.com/news_article/show/983839</ref>

==Honors==

'''Individual'''
* USL All-League Team: [[2016 USL season|2016]]

